Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.10,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}哼哼喘着粗气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:24.18,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}沿着走廊一阵风跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.31,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今晚是你最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:31.36,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}你想吃的就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.44,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}就是这个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:36.53,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}加上你就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:40.95,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}美食和大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:44.95,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
